## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9533a-177">仅在设计期间，通过对象模型以编程方式发出工作流实例时使用此属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9533a-177">This property is used only at design time, while programmatically emitting a workflow instance using the object model.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9533a-178">它表示引用事件处理程序但尚未编译的 XAML。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9533a-178">It represents XAML that references the event handler, which has not been compiled yet.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9533a-179">此属性包含一个带有事件名和事件处理程序名称/值对的 `Hashtable`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9533a-179">This property contains a `Hashtable`, with event name and event handler name-value pairs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9533a-180">编译之后，事件属性直接与处理程序关联。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9533a-180">After compilation, the event property is associated directly with the handler.</span></span>  
  
 [!INCLUDE[DependencyPropertyRemark](~/includes/dependencypropertyremark-md.md)]  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9533a-181">下面的示例演示如何设置 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty> 依赖属性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9533a-181">The following example shows how to set the value of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty> dependency property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
CodeActivity code1 = new CodeActivity();  
Hashtable eventsHashtable = new Hashtable();  
eventsHashtable.Add("ExecuteCode", "methodName1");  
code1.SetValue(WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty, eventsHashtable);  
```
